1
00:01:31,424 --> 00:01:32,240
=Blossoms of Power=

2
00:01:32,256 --> 00:01:35,140
(Adapted from the novel, After My
Bloom, All Flowers Wither by Jin Huang)

3
00:01:35,220 --> 00:01:38,180
=Episode 14=

4
00:01:38,300 --> 00:01:41,060
(Gudu Garden)

5
00:01:42,120 --> 00:01:42,560
Here.

6
00:01:42,560 --> 00:01:44,480
- Kick it to me.
- Brother, I want to play too.

7
00:01:45,648 --> 00:01:46,510
Thank you, Brother.

8
00:01:46,510 --> 00:01:48,000
Let me play!

9
00:01:49,430 --> 00:01:50,230
Nanny Liu.

10
00:01:52,040 --> 00:01:52,870
Nanny Liu,

11
00:01:53,200 --> 00:01:54,590
why is there bloody water?

12
00:01:55,790 --> 00:01:57,280
What a tragedy.

13
00:01:57,280 --> 00:01:59,040
One of the children is badly injured.

14
00:01:59,040 --> 00:02:00,200
Nanny, don't panic.

15
00:02:00,200 --> 00:02:01,568
I'll go take a look right now.

16
00:02:07,590 --> 00:02:09,910
You must be
Commandery Princess Zhaoning.

17
00:02:12,000 --> 00:02:13,400
How did you get hurt so badly?

18
00:02:13,800 --> 00:02:15,080
I am Qi Pei.

19
00:02:15,520 --> 00:02:16,910
From Li County, Shunan.

20
00:02:16,910 --> 00:02:19,150
My older brother owed gambling debts,

21
00:02:19,150 --> 00:02:21,150
and was thrown into prison
in Zenan District.

22
00:02:21,560 --> 00:02:23,080
But he never gambles.

23
00:02:25,240 --> 00:02:26,360
When I went to visit him,

24
00:02:26,910 --> 00:02:28,590
he had vanished into thin air.

25
00:02:28,840 --> 00:02:30,360
I sought help everywhere to no avail,

26
00:02:30,384 --> 00:02:32,656
so I had to come to the capital
to appeal to the Emperor.

27
00:02:33,120 --> 00:02:35,190
As a result, I was hunted down
all the way here.

28
00:02:35,328 --> 00:02:36,400
Do you have any evidence?

29
00:02:36,448 --> 00:02:38,192
The officials in Zenan
protect each other,

30
00:02:38,406 --> 00:02:39,526
and distort the truth.

31
00:02:39,870 --> 00:02:41,120
The evidence I collected

32
00:02:41,360 --> 00:02:43,240
was tricked out of me and destroyed.

33
00:02:51,470 --> 00:02:53,120
They must have caught up with me.

34
00:02:53,120 --> 00:02:54,630
Mo Yu, protect Qi Pei.

35
00:02:54,630 --> 00:02:55,560
We'll go out together.

36
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:56,470
Yes.

37
00:03:15,808 --> 00:03:17,080
There's tung oil in the water.

38
00:03:17,800 --> 00:03:19,470
These deranged thugs

39
00:03:19,470 --> 00:03:20,800
dare to commit crimes so openly!

40
00:03:34,710 --> 00:03:35,190
Hurry.

41
00:04:24,480 --> 00:04:25,950
Mo Yu, stay close to me!

42
00:04:25,950 --> 00:04:26,430
Yes.

43
00:04:27,920 --> 00:04:28,360
Come.

44
00:04:48,288 --> 00:04:50,310
- Protect His Highness!
- Protect His Highness!

45
00:04:50,310 --> 00:04:51,240
- The guards are here! Retreat!
- Hurry!

46
00:04:51,480 --> 00:04:52,630
- Hurry!
- Hurry!

47
00:04:52,630 --> 00:04:54,630
- Protect His Highness!
- Protect His Highness!

48
00:04:56,192 --> 00:04:57,600
Imperial Guards, hear my command!

49
00:04:57,680 --> 00:05:00,390
There are assassins
in the courtyard. Arrest them all.

50
00:05:00,400 --> 00:05:01,630
Don't let a single one escape.

51
00:05:02,240 --> 00:05:02,800
- Yes.
- Yes.

52
00:05:03,120 --> 00:05:03,600
Go!

53
00:05:09,888 --> 00:05:10,720
Commandery Princess!

54
00:05:10,928 --> 00:05:11,800
Commandery Princess!

55
00:05:13,720 --> 00:05:15,240
Qi Pei is a crucial witness.

56
00:05:15,800 --> 00:05:16,830
Keep him safe.

57
00:05:17,390 --> 00:05:18,000
Don't worry.

58
00:05:18,048 --> 00:05:19,160
Everything will be fine.

59
00:05:21,984 --> 00:05:22,830
Commandery Princess!

60
00:05:23,472 --> 00:05:24,310
Commandery Princess!

61
00:05:34,590 --> 00:05:35,160
Your Highness,

62
00:05:35,170 --> 00:05:36,800
Commandery Princess went
to Gudu Garden to care for the orphans,

63
00:05:36,800 --> 00:05:37,680
and encountered a fire.

64
00:05:39,680 --> 00:05:40,830
Where is she now?

65
00:05:40,830 --> 00:05:41,630
How is she doing?

66
00:05:41,830 --> 00:05:42,720
She was rescued.

67
00:05:42,720 --> 00:05:43,792
She is not seriously hurt.

68
00:05:44,270 --> 00:05:45,040
Who saved her?

69
00:05:45,104 --> 00:05:46,288
I will reward them handsomely.

70
00:05:47,480 --> 00:05:48,560
It was Prince Lie.

71
00:06:04,000 --> 00:06:04,992
Drink your medicine.

72
00:06:11,600 --> 00:06:13,000
The Duke's manor is heavily guarded,

73
00:06:14,000 --> 00:06:15,510
yet you can come and go as you please.

74
00:06:15,712 --> 00:06:17,560
It seems you are not only
in good health,

75
00:06:17,648 --> 00:06:19,190
but also highly skilled in martial arts.

76
00:06:27,310 --> 00:06:29,240
We are destined
to be husband and wife after all.

77
00:06:30,600 --> 00:06:32,640
Naturally, I have no need
to hide anything from you.

78
00:06:33,536 --> 00:06:34,512
Drink your medicine.

79
00:06:41,360 --> 00:06:43,560
Are you forcing me
to feed it to you with my lips?

80
00:06:45,830 --> 00:06:47,430
I never yield to threats.

81
00:07:16,240 --> 00:07:17,680
I have been very restrained.

82
00:07:20,000 --> 00:07:21,310
I don't want to offend you,

83
00:07:24,070 --> 00:07:25,600
nor do I want you to despise me.

84
00:07:25,750 --> 00:07:26,870
Xiao Huayong.

85
00:07:31,408 --> 00:07:34,120
Commandery Princess Zhaoning,
who always prioritizes the big picture,

86
00:07:34,830 --> 00:07:36,070
abandoned me

87
00:07:37,430 --> 00:07:38,750
to choose another.

88
00:07:41,070 --> 00:07:42,270
But who else

89
00:07:43,750 --> 00:07:45,160
is a better match for you than me,

90
00:07:48,390 --> 00:07:49,870
who has a legitimate imperial descent

91
00:07:50,680 --> 00:07:51,870
and a short life expectancy?

92
00:08:17,120 --> 00:08:18,390
Legitimate imperial descent

93
00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:19,800
can be changed.

94
00:08:22,560 --> 00:08:23,870
Whether your life is short or not

95
00:08:24,430 --> 00:08:25,360
can be orchestrated.

96
00:08:50,080 --> 00:08:50,790
Get out.

97
00:09:14,736 --> 00:09:16,336
Don't be angry, Commandery Princess.

98
00:09:17,270 --> 00:09:18,390
It's my fault.

99
00:09:20,360 --> 00:09:21,270
Get some good rest.

100
00:09:22,200 --> 00:09:23,960
I'll handle the rest.

101
00:09:25,030 --> 00:09:25,910
As for Changying,

102
00:09:27,320 --> 00:09:29,550
you don't need to thank him in person.

103
00:09:40,720 --> 00:09:41,390
Your Highness,

104
00:09:41,504 --> 00:09:44,112
aren't you just making the
Commandery Princess angry for nothing?

105
00:09:47,030 --> 00:09:48,320
When I heard she was in danger,

106
00:09:48,750 --> 00:09:49,840
I was worried sick.

107
00:09:50,630 --> 00:09:51,630
And I blamed myself,

108
00:09:52,240 --> 00:09:53,750
wishing I had been the one to save her.

109
00:09:57,200 --> 00:09:58,670
I felt so powerless and anxious

110
00:10:00,270 --> 00:10:01,840
that I lost my composure for a moment.

111
00:10:03,510 --> 00:10:04,480
In all these years,

112
00:10:05,320 --> 00:10:06,670
you've never been like this.

113
00:10:11,664 --> 00:10:12,910
Are we returning to the palace?

114
00:10:19,030 --> 00:10:19,870
No.

115
00:10:23,360 --> 00:10:24,600
We're going to deliver a gift.

116
00:10:28,300 --> 00:10:30,240
I happened to see her going
to Gudu Garden today,

117
00:10:30,630 --> 00:10:32,000
so I quietly followed her.

118
00:10:35,240 --> 00:10:36,960
At least I could be
a little closer to her.

119
00:10:38,440 --> 00:10:39,550
I didn't expect to save her.

120
00:10:47,480 --> 00:10:48,600
Changying,

121
00:10:49,910 --> 00:10:51,910
knowing the road ahead is doomed,

122
00:10:52,960 --> 00:10:54,600
yet still embracing it willingly...

123
00:10:54,976 --> 00:10:56,200
I understand that feeling, too.

124
00:11:01,150 --> 00:11:02,670
I won't try to persuade you anymore.

125
00:11:06,320 --> 00:11:07,270
I couldn't anyway.

126
00:11:10,390 --> 00:11:11,150
Changqing...

127
00:11:11,270 --> 00:11:11,840
Your Highness,

128
00:11:12,360 --> 00:11:13,390
the Crown Prince is here.

129
00:11:36,030 --> 00:11:37,390
Greetings, Your Highness.

130
00:11:38,200 --> 00:11:39,200
Greetings, Your Highness.

131
00:11:39,200 --> 00:11:40,240
We are brothers.

132
00:11:41,744 --> 00:11:42,864
No need for formalities.

133
00:11:48,460 --> 00:11:50,700
Your Highness, to what do we owe
the honor of your visit?

134
00:11:50,720 --> 00:11:51,970
Do you have any orders for us?

135
00:11:53,440 --> 00:11:55,510
I just came from Duke of Wei's Manor.

136
00:11:56,440 --> 00:11:57,910
The Commandery Princess asked me

137
00:11:57,910 --> 00:12:00,150
to thank you on her behalf
for saving her, Changying.

138
00:12:11,240 --> 00:12:13,200
This is between
the Commandery Princess and me.

139
00:12:15,030 --> 00:12:17,080
You did her a great favor.

140
00:12:17,088 --> 00:12:18,890
But men and women
should keep their distance.

141
00:12:18,960 --> 00:12:20,720
She wishes to avoid suspicion,

142
00:12:21,200 --> 00:12:22,270
which is why she asked me

143
00:12:22,720 --> 00:12:23,840
to thank you on her behalf.

144
00:12:28,600 --> 00:12:30,150
Since the gift has been delivered...

145
00:12:33,150 --> 00:12:33,790
There's no rush.

146
00:12:35,296 --> 00:12:37,456
This is Commandery Princess's gift
of gratitude.

147
00:12:38,080 --> 00:12:39,150
My gift of gratitude

148
00:12:39,720 --> 00:12:40,910
hasn't been delivered yet.

149
00:12:57,020 --> 00:12:58,780
(Minister Song...)

150
00:12:59,960 --> 00:13:03,120
This letter seems to be a secret missive
from Noble Consort Rong

151
00:13:03,120 --> 00:13:05,510
to win over court officials.

152
00:13:07,480 --> 00:13:10,240
Noble Consort Rong
is working so tirelessly

153
00:13:10,240 --> 00:13:12,030
to gather trusted followers
for you, Changying.

154
00:13:12,030 --> 00:13:14,120
What a deep bond between mother and son.

155
00:13:15,888 --> 00:13:17,510
But I fear it might carry the suspicion

156
00:13:18,000 --> 00:13:20,240
of forming factions for personal gain.

157
00:13:23,008 --> 00:13:25,072
Your Highness,
you're incredibly resourceful,

158
00:13:25,270 --> 00:13:27,550
but these letters are just
about trivial family matters.

159
00:13:28,000 --> 00:13:29,550
They hardly count as forming factions.

160
00:13:29,616 --> 00:13:31,670
And Changying knows absolutely nothing
about them.

161
00:13:32,240 --> 00:13:32,910
Is that so?

162
00:13:33,696 --> 00:13:36,390
But I have dozens
of such letters in my palace.

163
00:13:42,240 --> 00:13:43,270
I naturally believe

164
00:13:44,120 --> 00:13:45,320
what you say, Changqing.

165
00:13:46,320 --> 00:13:47,390
But will others

166
00:13:48,120 --> 00:13:48,870
believe it?

167
00:13:54,600 --> 00:13:56,440
As for this gift from you,

168
00:13:57,720 --> 00:13:59,240
Changying and I are deeply grateful.

169
00:14:01,030 --> 00:14:01,910
We accept it.

170
00:14:03,200 --> 00:14:03,870
Changqing.

171
00:14:17,840 --> 00:14:19,910
Whatever you two brothers intend to do,

172
00:14:20,910 --> 00:14:21,960
I won't interfere.

173
00:14:22,840 --> 00:14:23,960
But as for my woman,

174
00:14:28,000 --> 00:14:30,750
no one is allowed
to lay a finger on her.

175
00:14:34,840 --> 00:14:36,270
Farewell, Your Highness.

176
00:14:42,200 --> 00:14:43,550
Didn't I say it?

177
00:14:43,630 --> 00:14:44,840
We are brothers.

178
00:14:45,270 --> 00:14:46,440
No need for formalities.

179
00:14:55,240 --> 00:14:55,960
Changqing,

180
00:14:56,600 --> 00:14:58,200
these letters can't convict us.

181
00:14:58,440 --> 00:14:59,600
Why let him threaten us?

182
00:15:00,600 --> 00:15:03,320
The Crown Prince
usually just holds back.

183
00:15:03,670 --> 00:15:04,750
Even without these letters,

184
00:15:05,720 --> 00:15:07,200
he would have other ways

185
00:15:07,200 --> 00:15:08,440
to make you back down.

186
00:15:08,720 --> 00:15:10,600
You just have to steer clear
of him for now.

187
00:15:11,200 --> 00:15:12,080
However...

188
00:15:14,120 --> 00:15:14,870
However what?

189
00:15:15,750 --> 00:15:17,360
He came in such a hurry today

190
00:15:18,670 --> 00:15:20,390
and even used letters to threaten us.

191
00:15:20,870 --> 00:15:22,750
This shows that his marriage
with Zhaoning

192
00:15:22,870 --> 00:15:23,790
has hit a snag.

193
00:15:24,480 --> 00:15:26,440
Otherwise,
why would he go to such lengths?

194
00:15:30,960 --> 00:15:33,030
So he hasn't won
Zhaoning's heart either.

195
00:15:33,720 --> 00:15:36,030
The omnipotent Crown Prince

196
00:15:38,208 --> 00:15:40,128
is also just suffering
from unrequited love.

197
00:15:45,270 --> 00:15:45,910
Young Master,

198
00:15:46,272 --> 00:15:48,030
the witness sent
by the Commandery Princess

199
00:15:48,030 --> 00:15:48,870
has been settled in.

200
00:15:49,408 --> 00:15:50,790
Make sure he is well taken care of.

201
00:15:50,960 --> 00:15:52,120
There must be no mistakes.

202
00:15:52,160 --> 00:15:53,200
Rest assured, Young Master.

203
00:15:53,712 --> 00:15:55,390
Li County is under
Shunan's jurisdiction.

204
00:15:55,470 --> 00:15:56,672
I absolutely refuse to believe

205
00:15:56,680 --> 00:15:57,990
that under my father's governance,

206
00:15:58,010 --> 00:15:59,900
such a despicable crime
could happen in Shunan.

207
00:15:59,910 --> 00:16:01,200
Yes, I don't believe it either.

208
00:16:01,870 --> 00:16:02,480
But

209
00:16:02,670 --> 00:16:04,670
why are you packing your bags?

210
00:16:05,040 --> 00:16:07,390
I'm going back
to thoroughly investigate this matter.

211
00:16:07,456 --> 00:16:08,360
You're investigating?

212
00:16:08,432 --> 00:16:10,080
Isn't the imperial court
sending someone?

213
00:16:10,150 --> 00:16:11,240
Within the imperial court,

214
00:16:11,320 --> 00:16:13,600
there are many
who covet Shunan's military power.

215
00:16:13,620 --> 00:16:15,950
I know this better than anyone
from my years in the capital.

216
00:16:15,960 --> 00:16:17,270
This case is murky.

217
00:16:17,280 --> 00:16:18,576
If someone uses it as a pretext,

218
00:16:18,576 --> 00:16:20,910
manipulating the case behind the scenes
to target my father,

219
00:16:20,910 --> 00:16:22,440
by the time the court finishes
investigating and makes a final ruling,

220
00:16:22,450 --> 00:16:24,540
it will be too late.
I must find out the truth first.

221
00:16:24,720 --> 00:16:25,360
Young Master,

222
00:16:25,600 --> 00:16:26,630
I'll go with you.

223
00:16:26,630 --> 00:16:27,270
No need.

224
00:16:27,360 --> 00:16:28,656
I'll go alone and return quickly.

225
00:16:28,672 --> 00:16:30,360
Stay at the manor and cover for me.

226
00:16:30,416 --> 00:16:31,480
And protect the witness.

227
00:16:33,960 --> 00:16:34,670
Young Master,

228
00:16:34,840 --> 00:16:35,910
please be careful.

229
00:16:40,080 --> 00:16:41,568
Vice Minister of Imperial Observatory,

230
00:16:41,568 --> 00:16:42,480
(Receiving the Mandate
and Establishing the Foundation)

231
00:16:42,480 --> 00:16:46,080
I ordered you to choose
an auspicious day for the royal wedding.

232
00:16:46,320 --> 00:16:47,360
Do you have a result?

233
00:16:47,960 --> 00:16:49,200
Replying to Your Majesty,

234
00:16:49,200 --> 00:16:52,270
based on astrology and birth charts,

235
00:16:52,390 --> 00:16:55,270
I have selected a highly auspicious date
for the marriage.

236
00:16:55,550 --> 00:16:57,550
Please take a look, Your Majesty.

237
00:17:03,120 --> 00:17:04,070
Excellent.

238
00:17:05,790 --> 00:17:06,590
Huayong,

239
00:17:07,030 --> 00:17:07,830
Zhaoning,

240
00:17:08,480 --> 00:17:09,590
one month from now.

241
00:17:09,680 --> 00:17:12,440
This date is indeed an excellent choice.

242
00:17:12,790 --> 00:17:14,880
What do the two of you think?

243
00:17:15,640 --> 00:17:16,350
Your Majesty,

244
00:17:17,510 --> 00:17:18,920
a few days ago, I

245
00:17:18,920 --> 00:17:20,640
was frightened at Gudu Garden.

246
00:17:21,000 --> 00:17:23,160
I beseech Your Majesty
to postpone the wedding for me.

247
00:17:23,392 --> 00:17:25,070
Regarding the incident at Gudu Garden,

248
00:17:25,070 --> 00:17:26,350
as to who set the fire,

249
00:17:26,350 --> 00:17:28,980
Prefect of Jingzhao has already
ordered a thorough investigation.

250
00:17:29,070 --> 00:17:31,720
Commandery Princess Zhaoning,
you need not worry.

251
00:17:32,030 --> 00:17:32,680
Your Majesty,

252
00:17:33,030 --> 00:17:34,680
I am feeling extremely unwell.

253
00:17:34,800 --> 00:17:37,290
I have already asked the imperial
physician to help me recover.

254
00:17:37,720 --> 00:17:40,030
I truly cannot get married right now.

255
00:17:44,160 --> 00:17:46,110
Your Majesty, since that is the case,

256
00:17:46,120 --> 00:17:48,270
let's wait until
the Commandery Princess feels better.

257
00:17:48,336 --> 00:17:50,976
Marriage is a major event.
There is no need to rush it right now.

258
00:17:51,776 --> 00:17:54,240
Thank you for your understanding,
Your Highness.

259
00:17:55,510 --> 00:17:56,400
Very well.

260
00:17:57,240 --> 00:18:00,070
I respect your wishes.

261
00:18:00,440 --> 00:18:02,680
Once Commandery Princess Zhaoning
has recovered,

262
00:18:03,440 --> 00:18:04,480
Minister of Rites,

263
00:18:04,784 --> 00:18:06,320
Vice Minister of Imperial Observatory,

264
00:18:06,720 --> 00:18:08,880
choose another auspicious date.

265
00:18:09,264 --> 00:18:10,960
- Yes, Your Majesty.
- Yes, Your Majesty.

266
00:18:11,060 --> 00:18:12,070
Thank you, Your Majesty.

267
00:18:18,220 --> 00:18:22,660
(Ningze Prefecture, Zenan District)

268
00:18:22,680 --> 00:18:23,310
Officers,

269
00:18:23,488 --> 00:18:24,700
the vegetables are quite fresh.

270
00:18:24,710 --> 00:18:25,720
I picked them this morning.

271
00:18:25,720 --> 00:18:28,190
Wash them and deliver them
to the magistrate's office for us.

272
00:18:39,640 --> 00:18:40,680
You're new here, huh?

273
00:18:40,910 --> 00:18:42,944
Who told you
that you could set up a stall here?

274
00:18:43,680 --> 00:18:45,590
Officers, please have mercy.

275
00:18:45,664 --> 00:18:48,030
This is my only way
to make a living and feed my family.

276
00:18:48,030 --> 00:18:48,830
Cut the crap.

277
00:18:48,920 --> 00:18:49,550
Get out of here.

278
00:18:51,480 --> 00:18:51,880
You...

279
00:18:52,110 --> 00:18:53,136
What gives you the right?

280
00:18:53,152 --> 00:18:55,310
Why kick my things and chase me away?

281
00:18:55,328 --> 00:18:57,310
I have no one to rely on,
and my life is worthless.

282
00:18:57,310 --> 00:18:58,590
You won't let me do my only job!

283
00:18:58,590 --> 00:18:59,400
How will I survive?

284
00:18:59,400 --> 00:19:00,480
Arrest this unruly peasant!

285
00:19:00,496 --> 00:19:01,248
Hold on!

286
00:19:03,720 --> 00:19:05,590
In broad daylight,

287
00:19:07,070 --> 00:19:08,510
even if these vendors are at fault,

288
00:19:08,960 --> 00:19:10,480
as officers of the imperial court,

289
00:19:10,520 --> 00:19:12,704
how can you abuse your power
to bully people like this?

290
00:19:12,720 --> 00:19:15,430
Who are you? You dare meddle in
the affairs of the magistrate's office?

291
00:19:15,440 --> 00:19:16,750
I am but a humble scholar.

292
00:19:17,440 --> 00:19:19,240
Though I am an outsider
residing in Zenan,

293
00:19:19,290 --> 00:19:20,990
I absolutely cannot stand by
and watch you

294
00:19:21,070 --> 00:19:22,400
bully the commoners like this.

295
00:19:23,030 --> 00:19:24,720
There are so many troublemakers today.

296
00:19:25,030 --> 00:19:26,070
Take them all back.

297
00:19:26,144 --> 00:19:27,590
- Let's see if you're still this cocky
- How can you arrest people?

298
00:19:27,590 --> 00:19:29,200
when we get to the magistrate's office.

299
00:19:29,880 --> 00:19:30,750
What are you doing?

300
00:19:31,240 --> 00:19:32,070
I'm here to help you.

301
00:19:32,160 --> 00:19:33,110
Who asked for your help?

302
00:19:33,960 --> 00:19:34,720
Let go.

303
00:19:34,960 --> 00:19:35,400
Move.

304
00:19:37,030 --> 00:19:37,480
Hurry up.

305
00:19:37,920 --> 00:19:38,400
Faster.

306
00:19:41,110 --> 00:19:42,064
What are you looking at?

307
00:19:42,310 --> 00:19:43,070
Walk faster.

308
00:19:49,480 --> 00:19:50,440
Why were you

309
00:19:50,790 --> 00:19:52,550
causing trouble on the street

310
00:19:52,672 --> 00:19:54,112
and obstructing official duties?

311
00:19:54,310 --> 00:19:54,960
Officer,

312
00:19:55,350 --> 00:19:57,590
I ran out of travel money,
so I set up a stall to get by.

313
00:19:57,590 --> 00:19:59,000
I was just acting on impulse earlier

314
00:19:59,000 --> 00:20:00,160
and offended you officers.

315
00:20:00,160 --> 00:20:01,160
I admit I was wrong, okay?

316
00:20:01,160 --> 00:20:02,510
Don't play dumb with me.

317
00:20:02,750 --> 00:20:03,240
Speak.

318
00:20:04,070 --> 00:20:04,864
What's your name?

319
00:20:05,240 --> 00:20:06,030
Cui Ergou.

320
00:20:07,240 --> 00:20:08,110
Cui Ergou.

321
00:20:09,480 --> 00:20:10,070
And you?

322
00:20:10,760 --> 00:20:12,624
Lin Tieniu.
I am traveling here for my studies.

323
00:20:12,630 --> 00:20:14,352
I was overcome
with righteous indignation.

324
00:20:14,368 --> 00:20:16,820
That's why I spoke up to help.
I didn't mean to cause trouble.

325
00:20:16,830 --> 00:20:18,720
How many people are in your families?

326
00:20:18,790 --> 00:20:20,200
I'm the only one in my family.

327
00:20:20,960 --> 00:20:21,920
Back home,

328
00:20:21,920 --> 00:20:23,400
I have a bedridden elderly father.

329
00:20:23,830 --> 00:20:25,960
Do you have any relatives

330
00:20:25,960 --> 00:20:27,200
working in the government?

331
00:20:27,200 --> 00:20:28,000
- No.
- No.

332
00:20:28,350 --> 00:20:29,310
Anyone in the military?

333
00:20:29,310 --> 00:20:30,030
- No.
- No.

334
00:20:35,480 --> 00:20:36,200
You two

335
00:20:36,880 --> 00:20:38,240
blocked the road with your stall

336
00:20:38,350 --> 00:20:39,568
and obstructed official duties.

337
00:20:40,640 --> 00:20:41,750
It's not a major crime.

338
00:20:42,110 --> 00:20:43,400
We'll lock you up for three days

339
00:20:43,790 --> 00:20:44,750
as a warning to others.

340
00:21:20,070 --> 00:21:22,270
Cui Jinbai, I'm begging you.

341
00:21:22,480 --> 00:21:25,552
I admit I really shouldn't have pestered
you just to avoid the princess.

342
00:21:25,560 --> 00:21:27,110
You have your future,
your reputation.

343
00:21:27,110 --> 00:21:28,000
Don't want any of that anymore?

344
00:21:28,000 --> 00:21:29,160
Could you stop pestering me?

345
00:21:34,160 --> 00:21:35,480
Is this all you have to say to me?

346
00:21:35,590 --> 00:21:36,160
Yes.

347
00:21:36,440 --> 00:21:37,510
Then could I trouble you

348
00:21:37,510 --> 00:21:39,056
to actually listen to what I'm saying?

349
00:21:42,368 --> 00:21:43,960
I have read extensively since childhood.

350
00:21:44,288 --> 00:21:47,270
My family's teachings, the Four Bonds,
the Three Principles and Five Virtues

351
00:21:47,270 --> 00:21:48,880
have long been etched into my bones.

352
00:21:49,680 --> 00:21:50,680
I also resent myself.

353
00:21:52,160 --> 00:21:53,920
Why have I become so absurd
and ridiculous?

354
00:21:55,000 --> 00:21:56,720
I've tried to cut all ties with you.

355
00:21:57,310 --> 00:21:58,310
But I can't do it.

356
00:21:58,550 --> 00:21:59,830
Are you crazy?

357
00:21:59,830 --> 00:22:00,720
I am crazy.

358
00:22:05,552 --> 00:22:07,270
You're the one who made me lose my mind.

359
00:22:09,960 --> 00:22:10,830
To be reckless

360
00:22:12,350 --> 00:22:13,400
and willingly so.

361
00:22:27,184 --> 00:22:28,880
Why don't we take care
of business first?

362
00:22:29,100 --> 00:22:31,290
Let's investigate
this so-called wrongful imprisonment.

363
00:22:34,720 --> 00:22:36,070
If you were coming over to help me,

364
00:22:36,070 --> 00:22:37,712
why didn't you bring a few more people?

365
00:22:41,420 --> 00:22:42,656
Without His Majesty's decree,

366
00:22:42,680 --> 00:22:44,540
or official documents
from the imperial court,

367
00:22:44,550 --> 00:22:46,760
leaving the capital secretly
is already a serious crime.

368
00:22:47,136 --> 00:22:48,960
If I brought people here
and made a big scene,

369
00:22:49,536 --> 00:22:51,248
would I be helping you or harming you?

370
00:22:59,790 --> 00:23:00,720
You two,

371
00:23:01,160 --> 00:23:03,030
we're short on cells right now.

372
00:23:03,720 --> 00:23:05,480
You didn't commit any major offenses.

373
00:23:06,000 --> 00:23:07,440
So we're releasing you early.

374
00:23:07,520 --> 00:23:08,680
You can leave tomorrow night.

375
00:23:09,070 --> 00:23:10,550
Tomorrow night? Why so soon?

376
00:23:10,680 --> 00:23:12,880
What? You want to celebrate
the Chinese New Year here?

377
00:23:17,400 --> 00:23:19,350
Why would they let us go so easily?

378
00:23:20,200 --> 00:23:21,000
Could it be

379
00:23:21,350 --> 00:23:22,680
they have an ulterior motive?

380
00:23:30,960 --> 00:23:33,240
Just sign and fingerprint this,
and you can go.

381
00:23:37,980 --> 00:23:40,620
(Prisoners: Lin Tieniu, Cui Ergou)
(Guard on Duty: Zhao Wu)

382
00:23:57,110 --> 00:23:58,350
Hurry up down there.

383
00:23:58,352 --> 00:23:59,568
- Make it quick.
- Hurry up.

384
00:24:01,312 --> 00:24:02,550
You guys in the back, hurry up.

385
00:24:03,640 --> 00:24:04,880
Move it!

386
00:24:09,936 --> 00:24:10,960
Put some back into it!

387
00:24:11,440 --> 00:24:12,000
Hurry up!

388
00:24:18,240 --> 00:24:18,920
Hurry up!

389
00:24:20,750 --> 00:24:21,200
Move!

390
00:24:22,310 --> 00:24:22,960
Go, go, go!

391
00:24:23,168 --> 00:24:24,640
Move it! What are you looking at?

392
00:24:24,640 --> 00:24:25,030
Hurry up!

393
00:24:25,960 --> 00:24:26,510
Keep moving!

394
00:24:26,880 --> 00:24:27,350
Hurry up!

395
00:24:28,000 --> 00:24:29,030
You in the back, hurry up!

396
00:24:29,424 --> 00:24:30,550
Let me tell you something.

397
00:24:30,550 --> 00:24:31,510
You'd better behave.

398
00:24:35,550 --> 00:24:36,240
Hurry up!

399
00:24:38,590 --> 00:24:39,400
Hurry up!

400
00:24:40,070 --> 00:24:41,000
Stop dawdling!

401
00:24:45,680 --> 00:24:47,920
Hurry up, you guys in the back!

402
00:24:48,790 --> 00:24:50,000
Stop slacking off! Hurry up!

403
00:24:53,960 --> 00:24:54,590
I wouldn't dare!

404
00:24:55,200 --> 00:24:56,830
I'll never do it again!

405
00:24:57,070 --> 00:24:58,830
I'll never do it again!

406
00:25:04,480 --> 00:25:05,270
See that?

407
00:25:05,872 --> 00:25:07,680
That's what happens
when you try to escape.

408
00:25:08,440 --> 00:25:09,590
You'd better work hard.

409
00:25:10,110 --> 00:25:11,640
If anyone dares to run away,

410
00:25:12,310 --> 00:25:13,510
you'll be in for it.

411
00:25:14,480 --> 00:25:14,880
Move!

412
00:25:19,030 --> 00:25:20,640
You guys, over here.

413
00:25:20,920 --> 00:25:21,790
Grab your tools here.

414
00:25:22,880 --> 00:25:23,830
Hurry up!

415
00:25:24,310 --> 00:25:24,830
Hurry up!

416
00:25:27,790 --> 00:25:28,680
Hurry up!

417
00:25:30,240 --> 00:25:30,790
Mister...

418
00:25:32,250 --> 00:25:33,030
Where are you from?

419
00:25:33,030 --> 00:25:33,480
Mister,

420
00:25:33,880 --> 00:25:34,880
how did you end up here?

421
00:25:41,920 --> 00:25:43,880
Looks like we won't
get anything out of them.

422
00:25:44,640 --> 00:25:46,200
Don't worry. We'll find another chance.

423
00:25:48,240 --> 00:25:49,000
You there.

424
00:25:49,160 --> 00:25:49,680
You.

425
00:25:49,830 --> 00:25:50,480
Yes, you.

426
00:25:50,680 --> 00:25:51,510
Take off your shirt.

427
00:25:51,690 --> 00:25:52,480
Come work the forge.

428
00:25:56,680 --> 00:25:57,240
Sir,

429
00:25:57,680 --> 00:25:58,350
let me do it.

430
00:26:02,960 --> 00:26:05,200
First time I've seen someone
volunteer for this.

431
00:26:05,200 --> 00:26:06,736
My family used to run a blacksmith shop.

432
00:26:06,740 --> 00:26:08,340
I've been forging iron
since I was a kid.

433
00:26:08,350 --> 00:26:09,720
I'm not used to mining anyway.

434
00:26:11,110 --> 00:26:12,400
Alright, you're up.

435
00:26:13,400 --> 00:26:14,240
Take off your shirt.

436
00:26:14,480 --> 00:26:15,270
Get to the forge.

437
00:26:21,640 --> 00:26:22,240
Hurry up!

438
00:26:30,350 --> 00:26:31,270
Hurry up!

439
00:26:31,440 --> 00:26:32,240
Stop dawdling!

440
00:26:32,350 --> 00:26:33,160
Get to work!

441
00:26:35,110 --> 00:26:35,920
Hurry up!

442
00:26:36,000 --> 00:26:37,070
Put your back into it!

443
00:26:38,240 --> 00:26:38,720
Move!

444
00:26:46,200 --> 00:26:46,830
Move faster!

445
00:26:51,860 --> 00:26:54,940
(Duke of Wei's Manor)

446
00:26:57,790 --> 00:26:58,590
Your Highness,

447
00:26:58,750 --> 00:27:00,790
the Crown Prince
has sent another letter.

448
00:27:01,590 --> 00:27:02,310
Read it.

449
00:27:02,310 --> 00:27:03,960
"Day after day,

450
00:27:03,960 --> 00:27:06,440
thoughts of you linger in my heart.

451
00:27:06,550 --> 00:27:09,720
The mountains are green,
the sky is high, and the road is long.

452
00:27:09,830 --> 00:27:12,030
Yet there is no one to meet after dusk.

453
00:27:13,070 --> 00:27:13,480
A...

454
00:27:14,240 --> 00:27:15,880
A moment apart,

455
00:27:16,270 --> 00:27:18,270
and my spirit fades."

456
00:27:19,750 --> 00:27:20,550
Your Highness,

457
00:27:20,720 --> 00:27:22,480
you'd better read it yourself.

458
00:27:25,140 --> 00:27:26,860
(How can a slight unfurrowing of brows
erase the pain in my heart?)

459
00:27:27,350 --> 00:27:28,440
So mushy.

460
00:27:32,750 --> 00:27:33,440
Your Highness,

461
00:27:33,750 --> 00:27:35,480
Jin Shan says there's an urgent matter.

462
00:27:35,480 --> 00:27:36,592
He must see you in person.

463
00:27:37,830 --> 00:27:38,928
Did something happen to Lin?

464
00:27:38,930 --> 00:27:40,000
Your Highness, Young Master

465
00:27:40,010 --> 00:27:41,440
can't leave here without permission,

466
00:27:41,440 --> 00:27:43,536
so he secretly went
to Zenan District to investigate.

467
00:27:43,590 --> 00:27:44,550
Before leaving, he said

468
00:27:44,550 --> 00:27:47,152
if there's no news from him
within five days, he might be trapped.

469
00:27:47,260 --> 00:27:50,310
He also said you are the only person in
the entire imperial capital he trusts,

470
00:27:50,320 --> 00:27:51,712
and that we could ask for your help.

471
00:27:55,550 --> 00:27:56,200
Hurry up!

472
00:28:27,640 --> 00:28:28,240
Sit down.

473
00:28:28,320 --> 00:28:29,590
This should be more comfortable.

474
00:28:44,110 --> 00:28:45,680
Does the wound on your back hurt a lot?

475
00:28:48,110 --> 00:28:48,750
It's nothing.

476
00:28:49,510 --> 00:28:50,270
Just a flesh wound.

477
00:28:50,600 --> 00:28:51,880
It just looks scary, that's all.

478
00:29:01,000 --> 00:29:02,200
Come on, get up and eat!

479
00:29:02,200 --> 00:29:02,790
Get up!

480
00:29:04,680 --> 00:29:05,510
It's mine!

481
00:29:07,350 --> 00:29:08,160
It's mine!

482
00:29:08,160 --> 00:29:09,590
Leave some for me!

483
00:29:13,680 --> 00:29:14,590
Eat up.

484
00:29:15,750 --> 00:29:17,310
They capture people for slave labor

485
00:29:17,500 --> 00:29:18,880
and won't even give us a full meal.

486
00:29:19,960 --> 00:29:21,070
Those beasts.

487
00:29:23,600 --> 00:29:24,850
We still have to work tomorrow.

488
00:29:25,400 --> 00:29:26,240
Try to eat something.

489
00:29:26,310 --> 00:29:27,090
I have no appetite.

490
00:29:28,110 --> 00:29:29,680
I really didn't expect

491
00:29:29,880 --> 00:29:31,240
that in Shunan's territory,

492
00:29:31,480 --> 00:29:33,480
someone would dare
to illegally open a mine,

493
00:29:33,480 --> 00:29:34,480
forge weapons,

494
00:29:34,480 --> 00:29:35,550
and enslave prisoners.

495
00:29:35,632 --> 00:29:38,070
These are capital offenses
strictly forbidden by the court.

496
00:29:38,688 --> 00:29:41,280
Shunan's terrain is complex
and extremely difficult to control.

497
00:29:42,128 --> 00:29:43,640
For them to operate in such a place

498
00:29:44,240 --> 00:29:45,480
on such a massive scale,

499
00:29:45,664 --> 00:29:47,696
the forces behind them
must be formidable.

500
00:29:50,080 --> 00:29:52,180
Right now, conserving our strength
is what matters.

501
00:29:52,550 --> 00:29:53,550
You should eat something.

502
00:29:55,030 --> 00:29:56,160
I really have no appetite.

503
00:30:01,510 --> 00:30:02,310
You're injured.

504
00:30:03,120 --> 00:30:05,510
I practice martial arts year-round,
so I get injured often.

505
00:30:05,510 --> 00:30:07,568
I wouldn't have noticed
if you hadn't mentioned it.

506
00:30:11,210 --> 00:30:12,720
Don't make a big deal out of it, okay?

507
00:30:15,030 --> 00:30:16,200
In front of me,

508
00:30:16,920 --> 00:30:19,070
you don't have to be
the flawless Young Master Bu.

509
00:30:23,200 --> 00:30:23,640
Here.

510
00:30:32,030 --> 00:30:33,240
Everyone knows

511
00:30:33,440 --> 00:30:35,200
that I, Bu Shulin, am a playboy.

512
00:30:35,250 --> 00:30:37,440
I spend my time drinking, partying
and fooling around.

513
00:30:37,440 --> 00:30:38,656
I'm ignorant and incompetent.

514
00:30:42,070 --> 00:30:43,400
Take a good look for yourself.

515
00:30:46,600 --> 00:30:47,790
You, ignorant and incompetent?

516
00:30:50,820 --> 00:30:53,500
You were summoned to the capital
by imperial decree at age nine.

517
00:30:53,510 --> 00:30:55,070
You were essentially a hostage.

518
00:30:55,590 --> 00:30:56,640
Your every move

519
00:30:57,070 --> 00:30:59,160
influenced the court's judgment
of Shunan.

520
00:31:01,350 --> 00:31:02,510
Yet, at such a young age,

521
00:31:03,440 --> 00:31:05,440
you navigated alone among nobles,

522
00:31:05,472 --> 00:31:06,640
civil and military officials,

523
00:31:06,656 --> 00:31:07,760
and even around His Majesty.

524
00:31:07,824 --> 00:31:09,830
You never brought the slightest trouble
to Shunan.

525
00:31:12,480 --> 00:31:13,240
I know

526
00:31:13,952 --> 00:31:16,000
you have your own responsibilities
to shoulder.

527
00:31:17,960 --> 00:31:18,880
This responsibility

528
00:31:21,510 --> 00:31:22,550
is both admirable

529
00:31:24,160 --> 00:31:25,240
and heartbreaking.

530
00:31:31,712 --> 00:31:33,550
If you don't want me
sitting next to you,

531
00:31:35,160 --> 00:31:36,270
I can move further away.

532
00:31:39,880 --> 00:31:40,790
Get some sleep.

533
00:31:42,000 --> 00:31:42,990
I'll keep watch for you.

534
00:32:27,600 --> 00:32:28,160
Your Highness,

535
00:32:28,192 --> 00:32:29,630
Bu Shulin has gone missing in Zenan.

536
00:32:29,640 --> 00:32:31,104
Commandery Princess followed him.

537
00:32:32,440 --> 00:32:33,070
I'll go, too.

538
00:32:33,590 --> 00:32:35,510
No. You haven't fully recovered yet.

539
00:32:35,880 --> 00:32:37,616
Also, we still haven't
found the mastermind

540
00:32:37,620 --> 00:32:39,780
behind the assassins who attacked you
at the lantern festival.

541
00:32:39,790 --> 00:32:40,720
I'm afraid those people

542
00:32:40,720 --> 00:32:41,820
will try to harm you again.

543
00:32:41,830 --> 00:32:43,270
I've ordered Zhao Zhenghao
to keep investigating

544
00:32:43,270 --> 00:32:44,880
the connection
between those assassins and Li Yanhui.

545
00:32:44,880 --> 00:32:46,200
Prepare the carriage. We leave now.

546
00:32:46,200 --> 00:32:46,640
Yes.

547
00:32:58,240 --> 00:32:58,680
Come here.

548
00:33:08,270 --> 00:33:09,880
You memorized all the routes here?

549
00:33:10,960 --> 00:33:12,000
The scale of this place

550
00:33:12,000 --> 00:33:13,510
far exceeds a normal mine.

551
00:33:13,880 --> 00:33:15,960
The illegal forging of weapons
is undeniable proof.

552
00:33:16,270 --> 00:33:17,480
We need to escape quickly

553
00:33:17,480 --> 00:33:18,270
and get the word out

554
00:33:18,448 --> 00:33:19,680
to wipe out this den of thieves.

555
00:33:20,160 --> 00:33:21,720
But the paths here go in all directions.

556
00:33:21,824 --> 00:33:23,392
I can't believe you remembered them all.

557
00:33:25,350 --> 00:33:26,720
My brilliance

558
00:33:26,720 --> 00:33:28,070
is already known to you.

559
00:33:28,272 --> 00:33:30,200
So there's no need for me
to hide it anymore.

560
00:33:37,880 --> 00:33:39,240
If we start from here,

561
00:33:40,480 --> 00:33:42,070
we only need to take out two guards.

562
00:33:47,880 --> 00:33:50,200
Avoid the main mine shaft
and armory on the west side,

563
00:33:50,510 --> 00:33:51,920
and leave through the east passage.

564
00:33:52,030 --> 00:33:53,310
This is the shortest route.

565
00:33:54,400 --> 00:33:56,400
Your brilliance

566
00:33:57,310 --> 00:33:58,640
is on par with mine.

567
00:34:00,110 --> 00:34:01,070
We're quite a match.

568
00:34:33,960 --> 00:34:34,440
Let's go.

569
00:34:34,800 --> 00:34:35,800
Someone's escaping!

570
00:34:35,800 --> 00:34:36,550
After them!

571
00:34:37,320 --> 00:34:37,760
Hurry!

572
00:34:38,480 --> 00:34:39,280
Catch them!

573
00:34:39,800 --> 00:34:40,320
Hurry!

574
00:34:41,760 --> 00:34:42,280
Hurry!

575
00:34:48,920 --> 00:34:49,670
There they are!

576
00:34:49,670 --> 00:34:50,510
Catch them!

577
00:34:51,280 --> 00:34:51,960
Over there!

578
00:34:52,032 --> 00:34:53,280
There are too many of them!

579
00:34:53,360 --> 00:34:54,150
You go first.

580
00:34:54,150 --> 00:34:55,400
No, we leave together.

581
00:34:56,960 --> 00:34:57,670
Listen to me.

582
00:35:00,030 --> 00:35:00,480
Go!

583
00:35:07,710 --> 00:35:08,360
Stop!

584
00:35:08,550 --> 00:35:09,230
Don't run!

585
00:35:10,710 --> 00:35:11,280
Stop!

586
00:35:11,400 --> 00:35:12,030
Get him!

587
00:35:13,800 --> 00:35:15,510
- That's for running!
- That's for running!

588
00:35:20,030 --> 00:35:20,760
Here you go, sir.

589
00:35:21,190 --> 00:35:22,110
Your horse is ready.

590
00:35:30,880 --> 00:35:31,760
Who are you?

591
00:35:34,960 --> 00:35:36,260
I am

592
00:35:36,260 --> 00:35:38,440
(Tang Juan, Magistrate of Zenan)
Tang Juan, Magistrate of Zenan District.

593
00:35:38,672 --> 00:35:39,960
Magistrate of Zenan District?

594
00:35:41,070 --> 00:35:41,630
Guards,

595
00:35:41,840 --> 00:35:43,190
arrest this fugitive.

596
00:35:43,440 --> 00:35:44,360
Throw him in prison

597
00:35:44,380 --> 00:35:45,670
and interrogate him thoroughly.

598
00:35:46,000 --> 00:35:46,590
Yes, sir.

599
00:35:51,780 --> 00:35:54,340
(Zenan District Office)

600
00:35:57,760 --> 00:35:58,840
The Crown Prince?

601
00:36:00,304 --> 00:36:02,750
His Highness must have followed
Commandery Princess here.

602
00:36:06,660 --> 00:36:08,550
Wherever he is,
and whatever he thinks or does

603
00:36:08,550 --> 00:36:09,616
have nothing to do with us.

604
00:36:09,664 --> 00:36:11,008
We need to focus on our business.

605
00:36:17,840 --> 00:36:18,670
Prefect Yu.

606
00:36:19,070 --> 00:36:21,550
(Yu Zao, Prefect of Zenan)
This man is Marquis of Shunan's heir.

607
00:36:22,280 --> 00:36:23,710
How should we deal with him?

608
00:36:24,000 --> 00:36:26,190
Since he already knows about the mine,

609
00:36:27,550 --> 00:36:29,550
we can't give him the chance

610
00:36:30,000 --> 00:36:31,670
to spread the word.

611
00:36:31,670 --> 00:36:32,480
Silence him?

612
00:36:33,840 --> 00:36:36,000
But he's the heir
of the Marquis of Shunan.

613
00:36:36,230 --> 00:36:37,800
In Marquis of Shunan's Manor,

614
00:36:38,280 --> 00:36:39,480
he is the heir.

615
00:36:42,550 --> 00:36:44,670
In the Zenan prison,

616
00:36:45,480 --> 00:36:47,710
he's just a death row inmate.

617
00:36:49,190 --> 00:36:50,150
I understand.

618
00:36:50,670 --> 00:36:52,360
Prefect Yu, Magistrate Tang.

619
00:36:54,000 --> 00:36:55,000
The daughter of Duke Wei,

620
00:36:55,024 --> 00:36:56,580
Commandery Princess Zhaoning
has arrived.

621
00:36:56,590 --> 00:36:57,904
She is already in the front hall.

622
00:36:58,320 --> 00:36:59,840
Commandery Princess Zhaoning?

623
00:37:01,280 --> 00:37:02,760
Why is she here?

624
00:37:04,590 --> 00:37:05,840
What are you waiting for?

625
00:37:07,000 --> 00:37:08,550
I'll get it done immediately.

626
00:37:34,630 --> 00:37:36,360
It seems someone can't wait.

627
00:37:37,000 --> 00:37:37,920
If you kill me,

628
00:37:38,736 --> 00:37:40,480
have you thought
about the consequences?

629
00:37:41,480 --> 00:37:43,360
You must know who I am by now.

630
00:37:43,480 --> 00:37:45,630
If I die in your Zenan prison,

631
00:37:47,590 --> 00:37:49,070
do you think you can get away with it?

632
00:37:49,710 --> 00:37:51,190
Do you think your superiors

633
00:37:51,190 --> 00:37:53,070
will step up and take the blame

634
00:37:53,670 --> 00:37:55,710
or will they throw you
under the bus immediately

635
00:37:56,320 --> 00:37:58,480
as a scapegoat
to appease the Marquis's wrath

636
00:37:58,480 --> 00:38:00,630
and cover up all their crimes?

637
00:38:08,360 --> 00:38:10,000
It's not too late to stop now.

638
00:38:28,190 --> 00:38:29,360
No matter what you say,

639
00:38:29,630 --> 00:38:30,670
this engagement

640
00:38:31,000 --> 00:38:32,480
must be broken.

641
00:38:32,590 --> 00:38:33,600
You are bullying me again.

642
00:38:36,230 --> 00:38:38,770
♪A wall that collapses at a single push♪

643
00:38:40,070 --> 00:38:41,550
It doesn't matter if some things

644
00:38:42,150 --> 00:38:42,960
take a little longer.

645
00:38:43,630 --> 00:38:44,630
I'm willing to wait.

646
00:38:50,470 --> 00:38:53,410
♪I've hidden so many words♪

647
00:38:54,030 --> 00:38:56,830
♪Too reluctant to tell you♪

648
00:38:57,700 --> 00:39:04,670
♪So never uncover♪

649
00:39:04,860 --> 00:39:07,220
♪The sand that slips away
with one grasp♪

650
00:39:08,350 --> 00:39:11,080
♪The flower that withers
after one bloom♪

651
00:39:12,040 --> 00:39:17,380
♪Silently buried deep inside my heart♪

652
00:39:19,140 --> 00:39:21,960
♪Every answer I gave♪

653
00:39:22,760 --> 00:39:25,610
♪Was both bittersweet and absurd♪

654
00:39:26,400 --> 00:39:29,770
♪Hiding my tear-filled eyes
when I hurt you♪

655
00:39:30,030 --> 00:39:33,340
♪How hard it truly was?♪

656
00:39:36,310 --> 00:39:39,750
♪The wounds that healed
with just a little comfort♪

657
00:39:40,740 --> 00:39:43,070
♪The lies made whole
with a single embrace♪

658
00:39:44,340 --> 00:39:50,100
♪Pretending to be brave
as if I'd never been hurt♪

659
00:39:51,510 --> 00:39:54,640
♪It's a shame I never could♪

660
00:39:55,090 --> 00:39:58,100
♪Give you a moon in return♪

661
00:39:58,210 --> 00:40:04,850
♪With the same open heart you loved me♪

662
00:40:04,850 --> 00:40:08,520
♪I've crossed the wasteland of memories♪

663
00:40:09,390 --> 00:40:12,150
♪Never knowing I was lost♪

664
00:40:12,590 --> 00:40:15,720
♪Why don't you take me away?♪

665
00:40:16,160 --> 00:40:22,110
♪Lead me out of this endless game
of hide-and-seek♪

666
00:40:23,510 --> 00:40:27,060
♪You'll never♪

667
00:40:27,340 --> 00:40:36,810
♪Know how much I long to, long to♪

668
00:41:02,980 --> 00:41:06,460
(No animals were harmed
in the making of this film)
